== 推广与营销 ==

索尼为《血源诅咒》的推广与丹麦的GivBlod组织合作在当地推出了“捐血换游戏”的活动，每位捐血者可以获得一份免费的《血源诅咒》游戏，或一份其他指定的PlayStation 4游戏。<ref>[http://www.polygon.com/2015/3/20/8264113/donate-blood-get-a-free-copy-of-bloodborne-in-denmark Donate blood, get a free copy of Bloodborne in Denmark] {{Wayback|url=http://www.polygon.com/2015/3/20/8264113/donate-blood-get-a-free-copy-of-bloodborne-in-denmark |date=20150627043549 }}.Polygon.2015-03-20.[2015-03-29].</ref>

《血源诅咒》在日本首发第一周便卖出了152,567份实体版游戏<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.playstationlifestyle.net/2015/04/01/japanese-sales-chart-bloodborne-debuts-big-ps4-continues-rule-hardware/|title=Japanese Sales Chart: Bloodborne Debuts Big, PS4 Continues to Rule Hardware|accessdate=2017-02-19|author=Jason Dunning|date=2015-04-01|publisher=PlayStation LifeStyle.|archive-date=2015-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150405160556/http://www.playstationlifestyle.net/2015/04/01/japanese-sales-chart-bloodborne-debuts-big-ps4-continues-rule-hardware/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，为日本当周最热卖的游戏<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://gematsu.com/2015/04/media-create-sales-32315-32915|title=Media Create Sales: 3/23/15 – 3/29/15|accessdate=2017-02-19|author=Sal Romano|date=2015-04-01|publisher=Gematsu|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402092342/http://gematsu.com/2015/04/media-create-sales-32315-32915|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在英国，游戏首发后以22,500份仅次于《战地：硬仗》销售排名第二<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/battlefield-beats-bloodborne-in-uk-sales-charts/1100-6426253/|title=Battlefield Beats Bloodborne in UK Sales Charts|accessdate=2017-02-19|author=Eddie Makuch|date=2015-03-30|publisher=GameSpot|archive-date=2015-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150401235652/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/battlefield-beats-bloodborne-in-uk-sales-charts/1100-6426253/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在北美地区，尽管《血源诅咒》发售时已经接近月底，它仍成为三月份第二畅销的游戏<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://venturebeat.com/2015/04/16/march-2015-npd-ps4-xbox-one/|title=March 2015 NPD: PS4 beats Xbox One; Battlefield, Bloodborne lead sluggish March game sales|accessdate=2017-02-19|author=JEFF GRUBB|date=2015-04-16|publisher=VentureBeat|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308151518/https://venturebeat.com/2015/04/16/march-2015-npd-ps4-xbox-one/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年4月5日，索尼公司与From Software宣布《血源诅咒》在全球已销售超过100万份<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.vg247.com/2015/04/14/bloodborne-one-million-ps4/|title=Bloodborne has sold-through one million units since launch|accessdate=2017-02-19|author=Stephany Nunneley|date=2015-04-05|publisher=VG247|archive-date=2015-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150416002817/http://www.vg247.com/2015/04/14/bloodborne-one-million-ps4/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，到9月时，其销售数量已超过200万份<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/ps4s-bloodborne-sells-2-million/1100-6430572/|title=PS4's Bloodborne Sells 2 Million|accessdate=2017-02-19|author=Eddie Makuch|date=2015-09-15|publisher=GameSpot|archive-date=2015-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150917231820/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/ps4s-bloodborne-sells-2-million/1100-6430572/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而早在发售之初，索尼便表明游戏的销量远超过了他们的预期<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/bloodborne-sales-surprised-sony/1100-6427389/|title=Bloodborne Sales Surprised Sony|accessdate=2017-02-19|author=Emanuel Maiberg|date=2015-05-16|publisher=GameSpot|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518202128/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/bloodborne-sales-surprised-sony/1100-6427389/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。


